JS:- make it more interactive ourt web-pages.
 Everything in JavaScript, happens inside an Execution-Context.
 Execution-Context:- It has 2 component
   Memory Component(Variable environment):-This is the place, all variables & function are stored. as a Key:Value paire.
   Code Component(Thread of Execution):- This is the place, where code is executed, one line at a time.

Call Stack:-
  Whenever E-C is created, it is pushed into the stack,
  Whenever E-C is deleted, it will move out of the stack.
  
  "Call Stack maintains the, order of execution of, Execution-Context"
  
  Call-Stack also known as:-
    Execution-Context Stack.
    Program Stack.
    Control Stack.
    Runtime Stack.
    Machine Stack.
